 FindSpecialStrings←{
⍝ Use this to search for stuff like "⍝CHECK⍝" or "⍝TODO" (⍵).
⍝ Without left argument the search starts in #.
     ⍺←#
     start←⍺
     r←⍉1↓[1]⎕SE.UCMD'locate ',⍵,' -return=count -objects=',⍕start
     r←(0<r[;1])⌿r
     r[;0]←{2>'#'+.=⍵:⍵ ⋄ {⌽⍵↑⍨1+⍵⍳'#'}⌽⍵}¨r[;0]
     1=⍴⎕XSI:r   ⍝ Called in the session?!
     r←(r[;0]≢¨⎕XSI[1])⌿r
     r
 }
